newsitem.title: NETHERLANDS: European feeds remain quietly in afternoon.
newsitem.headline: European feeds remain quietly in afternoon.

text.p: Business on the European meals and feeds market remained quietly this afternoon with only a handful of trades reported on nearby positions, dealers said.

"There was little faith in the market and only a few hand-to-mouth trades were reported. The absence of many operators visiting a grain bourse in Hamburg and an easier Chicago soymeal futures opening kept a lid on activity today," one broker said.
Arrived Argentine soymeal pellets traded at $282 a tonne cif Rotterdam, arrived and Sept Argentine sunmeal pellets changed hands at $159 a tonne cif Rotterdam.--KAREL LUIMES +31 20 504 5832
